Charcoal mod
============

Adds charcoal lumps.
Charcoal lumps behaves like coal lumps but can be created by burning tree or jungletree in the furnance.


Copyright (c) 2012 Gal Buki <torusJKL@gmail.com>


Installation
------------
Copy the folder into ~/.minetest/mods/mintest/

